  <str key="2976290447-ucdt" type="ucdt" originalKey="2976290447">&lt;font size="28"&gt;Summer fun returns to Auraxis!&lt;br&gt;To celebrate this event, we have prepared a few event directives.&lt;br&gt;The first one is:&lt;br&gt; &lt;font color="#ACE1E5"&gt;Operation: Ares&lt;/font&gt; available 8th July - 10th August&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt; Take to the deserts of Indar with the &lt;font color="#ACE1E5"&gt;Indarian Scout Helmet&lt;/font&gt; and &lt;font color="#ACE1E5"&gt;Indarian Scout Armor&lt;/font&gt;! Available for limited time on the &lt;font color="#ACE1E5"&gt;Depot&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Complete the &lt;font color="#ACE1E5"&gt;Operation: Ares&lt;/font&gt; Event Directive to earn summer themed rewards such as:&lt;br&gt;&lt;font size="28" color="#ACE1E5"&gt; &amp;#8226; Indarian Scout Decal&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font size="28" color="#ACE1E5"&gt; &amp;#8226; Indarian Scout Title&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font size="28" color="#ACE1E5"&gt; &amp;#8226; Indarian Scout Banner&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font size="28" color="#ACE1E5"&gt; &amp;#8226; Indarian Scout Banner Frame&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font size="28" color="#ACE1E5"&gt; &amp;#8226; Lightning Storm Camo&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font size="28" color="#ACE1E5"&gt; &amp;#8226; Desert Fennec Hood Ornament&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;Follow the news to get ready to the second directive later!</str>
  <str key="3046205420-ucdt" type="ucdt" originalKey="3046205420">Designed for the harsh deserts of Indar, this combat armor combines lightweight protection with an integrated liquid-cooling system. Reinforced armor plates shield the wearer from enemy fire, while exposed cooling tubes circulate coolant to help maintain peak performance in extreme heat.&lt;font color="#dc9c36"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This armor can only be worn by VS Engineers.&lt;/font&gt;</str>
